Privacy Policy for Arcana

This Privacy Policy governs the collection, use, and sharing of personal information by Arcana, a Discord bot developed by Kizura Amberfang. By using Arcana, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

Information We Collect

We collect information that you provide to us through your use of the bot, such as your Discord user ID and username, server and channel information, and message content.

We use your information to give you the possibility to storage in the database 1 deck per user per channel. To delete the data you can just shuffle the deck.
